  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. The slope is (28 \u2212 3)/(5 \u2212 0) = 25/5 = 5. Since the line passes through (0, 3), the <em>y</em>-intercept is 3. Therefore <em>f</em>(<em>x</em>) = 5<em>x</em> + 3.</p><p>Choices A, B, and C are incorrect; they result from using incorrect slope or intercept values.</p>",
